                      ʾabba
                        Baḥrǝyä Śǝllāse is mentioned as the scribe in the colophon and in
                        supplication formulas.
 The Ms. is written in the same hand as Mss.
                        MQM-012 and MQM-013.<date>Second half of the 20th century.</date>
