                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; name of the protagonist; names of the
                           donors; incipit of all sections and subsections; a few other words like
                           ḥawarya "apostle"; elements of the punctuation signs and of the text
                           dividers; elements of Ethiopic numerals.
 On the incipit page of
                           Texts I-1 and I-2 (fols. 3r, 45r) several groups of lines are
                           rubricated.</seg>
                     </handNote>
